## System Requirements

bayescan function  requires software Bayescan 2.1 installed in your computer. bayescan tries to guess the name of the executable program depending on the operating system. Specifically, the followings are used: "bayescan_2.1" under Linux (installed from sources), or "C:/Program Files/BayeScan2.1/binaries/BayeScan2.1_win32bits_cmd_line.exe" under Windows.

